---
---
<section class="section-pad" id="cases">
  <div class="section-head reveal">
    <div>
      <div class="label">§ 03 / Case studies</div>
      <h2>Results <span class="italic-serif">on tape</span>.</h2>
    </div>
    <p>Two current clients. Numbers, not adjectives.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="case-list">
    <a class="case reveal" href="https://cassieschoonover.com/orderpending1u1m-b" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <span class="idx">01</span>
      <span class="client-mark">C</span>
      <span class="client-name">Cassie Schoonover</span>
      <span class="role">Course grade · VSL · reels</span>
      <span class="stat"><b><span class="curr">$</span>8K+</b> course revenue · week 1</span>
      <span class="arrow">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4">
          <path d="M3 11 L11 3 M5 3 H11 V9"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
    </a>
    <a class="case reveal" href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DTK_xIYCNiS/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
      <span class="idx">02</span>
      <span class="client-mark tight">CMD</span>
      <span class="client-name">CMD Careers</span>
      <span class="role">Grade · edit · content lead</span>
      <span class="stat"><b>Top performers</b> on the channel</span>
      <span class="arrow">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4">
          <path d="M3 11 L11 3 M5 3 H11 V9"/>
        </svg>
      </span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.case-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

.case {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 44px 56px 1fr 1.1fr 1fr auto;
  gap: 24px;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 24px 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(246,233,201,0.12);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: padding 0.3s, background 0.3s;
}
.case:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(246,233,201,0.12); }
.case:hover {
  padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px;
  background: rgba(252,175,23,0.06);
}
.case:hover .arrow { background: #fcaf17; color: #120905; transform: rotate(-45deg); }

.idx { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #766652; letter-spacing: 0.14em; font-weight: 500; }

.client-mark {
  width: 56px; height: 56px;
  border: 1.5px solid rgba(246,233,201,0.32);
  background: #1d1109;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  overflow: hidden;
  color: #fcaf17;
  font-family: "Alfa Slab One", "Times New Roman", serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  text-shadow: 0 0.06em 0 #961e10;
  letter-spacing: 0; line-height: 1; padding: 0 4px;
}
.client-mark.tight { font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }

.client-name {
  font-family: "Times New Roman", Times, serif;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-size: clamp(22px, 2.2vw, 32px);
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  color: #f6e9c9;
  text-transform: none;
  line-height: 1;
}
.role, .stat {
  font-family: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, Menlo, monospace;
  font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #b9a88a; font-weight: 500;
}
.stat { font-size: 13px; }
.stat b {
  color: #961e10; font-weight: 300; font-size: 24px;
  font-family: "Alfa Slab One", "Times New Roman", serif;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-shadow: none; margin-right: 0.5em;
}
.curr { margin-right: 0.2em; }

.arrow {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  border: 1px solid #961e10;
  border-radius: 999px;
  display: grid; place-items: center;
  color: #961e10;
  transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
}

@media (max-width: 860px) {
  .case { grid-template-columns: 40px 48px 1fr auto; gap: 14px; }
  .role, .stat { display: none; }
  .client-mark { width: 48px; height: 48px; }
}
</style>
